    {
      "id": "nctGBbAtSwZ09Pv27iNGK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1286.3859997466539,
      "y": 1256.8755388656268,
      "width": 921.7393798828125,
      "height": 625,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bhH",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1650832587,
      "version": 613,
      "versionNonce": 1475026565,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783678607179,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Collect metrics:\n1. how to collect metrics\nMetrics Collect agent collects metrics from each pod of a service and continiously send to MQ\nmetric collect push vs pull?\npush:\nservices push metrics to agent\npull: \nagent pull data from services via API call\n\nI would go ahead with pull, better monitoring via GET /metrics\n\n2. send metrics sync vs async?\nasync better for fault torent\n\nDB?\n\naccess pateern :\nwrite heavy: 10 m writes ps\n\noptions\n1. SQL : not optimized for writes\n2. NoSQL : optimized for write, high learning curve\n3. custom: TSDB like influxDB or prometheus ( preferred)\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Collect metrics:\n1. how to collect metrics\nMetrics Collect agent collects metrics from each pod of a service and continiously send to MQ\nmetric collect push vs pull?\npush:\nservices push metrics to agent\npull: \nagent pull data from services via API call\n\nI would go ahead with pull, better monitoring via GET /metrics\n\n2. send metrics sync vs async?\nasync better for fault torent\n\nDB?\n\naccess pateern :\nwrite heavy: 10 m writes ps\n\noptions\n1. SQL : not optimized for writes\n2. NoSQL : optimized for write, high learning curve\n3. custom: TSDB like influxDB or prometheus ( preferred)\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "6ytYefARSEcclDRXlSgCd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2260.848853015355,
