      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Where to aggregate:\n1. COllection agent\n2. DB\n3. During fetch\n\nall options are valid and need to be implemented for diff use cases\n\n\n\n2. Send alerts:\n\ndata writen in db gets aggregated for alerts and dashboards\n\n3. dashboard:\npromQL\n\nspace optimisations:\nrun length encoding\ncompression\ndown sampling\ncold storage for arcival\n\nTSDB stores data like this\nSeries\n\ncpu_usage\nhost=A\n\ntimestamps:\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\nvalues:\n40\n42\n43\n41\n\nimproves compression",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Where to aggregate:\n1. COllection agent\n2. DB\n3. During fetch\n\nall options are valid and need to be implemented for diff use cases\n\n\n\n2. Send alerts:\n\ndata writen in db gets aggregated for alerts and dashboards\n\n3. dashboard:\npromQL\n\nspace optimisations:\nrun length encoding\ncompression\ndown sampling\ncold storage for arcival\n\nTSDB stores data like this\nSeries\n\ncpu_usage\nhost=A\n\ntimestamps:\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\nvalues:\n40\n42\n43\n41\n\nimproves compression",
